    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316610/extras/bfd4a7d8520b5fa738654a76798772c8.poster.avif?t=1771551382\" width=700 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316610/extras/bfd4a7d8520b5fa738654a76798772c8.webm?t=1771551382\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316610/extras/bfd4a7d8520b5fa738654a76798772c8.mp4?t=1771551382\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The universe is dying, galaxy after galaxy but capitalism won’t wait. On board your ship, your employer S-Corp expects you to meet revenue targets by exploiting every star system in your path. After all, just because the stars are fading away doesn’t mean business has to stop.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316610/extras/6f94dff4a7f662294ec898c58e4f0038.avif?t=1771551382\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316610/extras_big/6f94dff4a7f662294ec898c58e4f0038.avif?t=1771551382 width=800 height=158 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore a procedurally generated galaxy</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each expedition takes place in a brand new procedurally generated galaxy. As a captain hired by S-Corp, your mission is simple : generate as much profit as possible. Survive, stay profitable and keep your shareholders happy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Exploit everything in your path</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You only have 10 days to complete your mission, so make the most of this valuable time with your automated production facilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Expand the colony networ</strong>k</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To expand the corporation’s commercial empire, you will need to visit stars and planets so that resource exploitation infrastructure can be deployed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316610/extras/2890377970b0884c10e3b0250aac45c5.poster.avif?t=1771551382\" width=700 height=318 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316610/extras/2890377970b0884c10e3b0250aac45c5.webm?t=1771551382\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316610/extras/2890377970b0884c10e3b0250aac45c5.mp4?t=1771551382\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Beware of the scourge that plagues the universe</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An elusive entity is slowly taking over the galaxy. You will have to carve your way through or face its minions and send them back to where they came from with a blast of laser.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Make smart decisions</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every action you take advances time and gradually increases the game’s difficulty. So think twice before you act.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316610/extras/fe1d57af88e4d8485c54a72d61a82655.poster.avif?t=1771551382\" width=700 height=318 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316610/extras/fe1d57af88e4d8485c54a72d61a82655.webm?t=1771551382\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316610/extras/fe1d57af88e4d8485c54a72d61a82655.mp4?t=1771551382\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Optimize your ship</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each battle strengthens your ship, and discoveries made across the galaxy can influence your chances of victory. And if you're in a bind, you can always visit your favorite coworker Bogg, who will gladly sell you upgrades at outrageous prices.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fast and accessible gameplay</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With streamlined controls and simplified 4X mechanics, exploration, expansion, and exploitation are just a few clicks away.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316610/extras/b1974a36b9cdd3c703f3bb1e8c3061be.avif?t=1771551382\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316610/extras_big/b1974a36b9cdd3c703f3bb1e8c3061be.avif?t=1771551382 width=800 height=142 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >~1 hour per expedition in a dying galaxy</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tens of thousands of stars waiting to be exploited</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple captains and starting weapons to shape your strategy</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Various types of cosmic monsters standing in your way</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Progressive upgrades earned through combat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Narrative events to refine your path to victory</p></li></ul>",
